WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Created by ©Yozuki  |  #VisitUs  t.me/Yozukilk

2
00:00:06.780 --> 00:00:10.270
Princess, time for some torture!

3
00:00:10.960 --> 00:00:13.400
For today's torture, we have a hamster!

4
00:00:13.590 --> 00:00:15.340
A hamster?

5
00:00:15.340 --> 00:00:17.100
This isn't good, Ex!

6
00:00:17.100 --> 00:00:18.960
I love hamsters.

7
00:00:18.960 --> 00:00:21.240
Don't beat me to the punch!

8
00:00:21.510 --> 00:00:23.650
It's true, though.

9
00:00:23.650 --> 00:00:26.130
I love hamsters.

10
00:00:26.500 --> 00:00:28.460
Their adorable faces...

11
00:00:29.060 --> 00:00:31.050
Their plump tushies...

12
00:00:31.050 --> 00:00:33.260
And most of all, how tiny they are!

13
00:00:34.460 --> 00:00:38.020
Such lovable, yet fragile animals...

14
00:00:38.020 --> 00:00:40.960
I bet they'd die if they 
were up against a lion.

15
00:00:40.960 --> 00:00:42.920
Most animals would.

16
00:00:43.260 --> 00:00:45.890
Looks like this one's in the bag!

17
00:00:45.890 --> 00:00:47.200
Come on out!

18
00:00:47.200 --> 00:00:49.440
Hamungous the hellbeast hamster!

19
00:00:55.580 --> 00:00:57.140
It's huge.

20
00:02:26.250 --> 00:02:28.000
'Tis Time for "Torture,"
Princess

21
00:02:32.890 --> 00:02:34.920
Huh? What?

22
00:02:34.920 --> 00:02:36.710
A lukewarm reception?

23
00:02:36.710 --> 00:02:40.930
Hamungous is a hellbeast hamster who's 
a star in the Demon World.

24
00:02:40.930 --> 00:02:43.510
Even His Majesty is a Hamungous fan!

25
00:02:44.090 --> 00:02:46.140
So intimidating...

26
00:02:46.400 --> 00:02:50.260
<i>Hamsters' eyes are huge 
when they're this size!</i>

27
00:02:50.770 --> 00:02:52.500
I mean, well...

28
00:02:52.500 --> 00:02:54.280
It's kind of scary.

29
00:02:55.300 --> 00:02:56.600
That hurts.

30
00:02:56.600 --> 00:02:57.810
You can talk?

31
00:02:58.100 --> 00:03:01.290
Hellbeast hamsters can talk.

32
00:03:01.290 --> 00:03:02.480
Krall.

33
00:03:02.480 --> 00:03:05.450
Unfortunately, I won't 
be giving in today.

34
00:03:05.450 --> 00:03:08.310
I'm sorry that I won't be confessing.

35
00:03:08.310 --> 00:03:09.650
Why are you apologizing for that?

36
00:03:10.000 --> 00:03:13.390
Really? Too bad.

37
00:03:13.390 --> 00:03:14.990
Let's get going, Hamungous.

38
00:03:15.310 --> 00:03:17.000
Please wait!

39
00:03:17.000 --> 00:03:21.260
Krall put her trust in me 
by bringing me along for this torture.

40
00:03:21.260 --> 00:03:23.540
She's helped me out so much.

41
00:03:23.540 --> 00:03:26.850
I don't want her torture 
to end in failure because of me!

42
00:03:26.850 --> 00:03:27.930
Hamungous!

43
00:03:28.270 --> 00:03:30.230
Please give me a chance!

44
00:03:30.230 --> 00:03:32.690
Oh? A chance, you say?

45
00:03:32.690 --> 00:03:36.110
Do you have a trick up 
your sleeve to make me fold?

46
00:03:36.110 --> 00:03:39.950
Yes! I can make a mean pepper steak!

47
00:03:51.570 --> 00:03:52.880
Wh-What?!

48
00:04:00.370 --> 00:04:04.370
Pro hamsters are usually signed 
to a talent agency.

49
00:04:04.660 --> 00:04:06.760
Hamungous, on the other hand...

50
00:04:06.760 --> 00:04:12.380
first blew up on social media and became 
a top pro hamster while staying freelance!

51
00:04:13.140 --> 00:04:15.400
Freelance
Pro Hamster

52
00:04:14.100 --> 00:04:15.400
Hamungous

53
00:04:14.100 --> 00:04:15.400
Hamungous

54
00:04:15.390 --> 00:04:17.060
A pro hamster?

55
00:04:17.060 --> 00:04:18.940
You can go pro as a hamster?

56
00:04:22.100 --> 00:04:25.280
<i>Nothing I hear or see makes any sense, 
so my brain can't keep up!</i>

57
00:04:25.280 --> 00:04:27.630
That smells amazing!

58
00:04:27.890 --> 00:04:29.900
It looks pretty authentic.

59
00:04:29.900 --> 00:04:30.880
Yep.

60
00:04:31.300 --> 00:04:35.360
Before making it big, Hamungous worked 
at a Chinese restaurant!

61
00:04:35.360 --> 00:04:38.210
And I hear all the ingredients 
were carefully selected.

62
00:04:38.210 --> 00:04:40.550
I can't wait!

63
00:04:45.380 --> 00:04:46.790
Order up.

64
00:04:50.530 --> 00:04:52.380
Time to dig in!

65
00:05:04.970 --> 00:05:06.560
It's delicious!

66
00:05:06.560 --> 00:05:08.140
You betcha!

67
00:05:08.140 --> 00:05:09.520
The rice is complimentary!

68
00:05:09.520 --> 00:05:11.150
And comes with unlimited refills!

69
00:05:11.750 --> 00:05:13.340
Awesome!

70
00:05:14.220 --> 00:05:19.590
<i>"So much for the hamster part," 
Ex silently thought to himself.</i>

71
00:05:21.130 --> 00:05:23.590
The princess 
confessed

72
00:05:24.660 --> 00:05:25.970
What?!

73
00:05:25.970 --> 00:05:27.850
Is this true?

74
00:05:28.070 --> 00:05:29.000
Indeed.

75
00:05:29.300 --> 00:05:32.430
I-I don't believe it.

76
00:05:33.150 --> 00:05:36.690
Hamungous was here for today's torture?

77
00:05:36.690 --> 00:05:38.480
Wish I could've been there.

78
00:05:38.480 --> 00:05:40.890
I thought you would say that.

79
00:05:40.890 --> 00:05:41.800
What?

80
00:05:42.800 --> 00:05:44.440
You don't mean...

81
00:05:44.440 --> 00:05:46.730
I had them take the time to stop by.

82
00:05:46.730 --> 00:05:48.240
Here's Hamungous!

83
00:05:51.420 --> 00:05:53.410
Hell yes!

84
00:05:58.280 --> 00:06:01.540
Oh, you got a photo with Hamungous?

85
00:06:03.190 --> 00:06:04.550
Are you jealous?

86
00:06:04.550 --> 00:06:07.470
Hamungous took part in today's torture.

87
00:06:07.470 --> 00:06:08.700
Oh?

88
00:06:09.860 --> 00:06:12.560
You should show Maomao-chan tomorrow.

89
00:06:15.150 --> 00:06:19.080
She might get mad and say, 
"Not fair, Papa!"

90
00:06:22.400 --> 00:06:23.890
<i>The next day.</i>

91
00:06:24.610 --> 00:06:26.810
<i>The Hell-Lord got yelled at.</i>

92
00:06:28.280 --> 00:06:32.280
Resume

93
00:06:28.280 --> 00:06:32.280
Furigana:      Hamungous Starham

94
00:06:28.280 --> 00:06:32.280
Name:             Hamungous Starham

95
00:06:28.280 --> 00:06:32.280
Birthday:                         8/7

96
00:06:28.280 --> 00:06:32.280
'Tis Time for "Torture,"
Princess

97
00:06:28.520 --> 00:06:31.930
<i>Yes! I can make a mean pepper steak!</i>

98
00:06:32.920 --> 00:06:36.160
Princess, for today's torture...

99
00:06:38.360 --> 00:06:40.030
You're up against me!

100
00:06:40.990 --> 00:06:42.660
I-Is that...

101
00:06:42.660 --> 00:06:43.920
That's right.

102
00:06:43.920 --> 00:06:46.600
One of the items 
from my Hellblade collection:

103
00:06:46.600 --> 00:06:48.420
Shishio, the Flaming Longsword!

104
00:06:46.800 --> 00:06:49.670
Shishio, the Flaming Longsword

105
00:06:46.800 --> 00:06:49.670
Shishio, the Flaming Longsword

106
00:06:49.950 --> 00:06:52.520
Packing enough heat 
to melt through shields and armor,

107
00:06:52.520 --> 00:06:57.790
this prized sword was the favorite 
of the departed god of destruction, Kyna!

108
00:06:58.090 --> 00:07:00.480
I'll be using this to make you surrender.

109
00:07:00.480 --> 00:07:01.970
Stop, you fiend!

110
00:07:01.970 --> 00:07:04.230
What are you going to do 
to Her Highness with that?!

111
00:07:09.430 --> 00:07:10.840
Fried rice!

112
00:07:11.330 --> 00:07:15.460
Krall told me that the princess 
gave in yesterday to pepper steak.

113
00:07:15.460 --> 00:07:19.000
Oh, so that really didn't 
count as the hamster?

114
00:07:19.000 --> 00:07:23.290
Today's torture is fried rice made 
with Shishio's supernatural heat!

115
00:07:23.560 --> 00:07:25.970
Will you be able to withstand 
its devastating power?

116
00:07:25.970 --> 00:07:28.970
Looks good...

117
00:07:29.850 --> 00:07:31.850
But rest assured, Ex!

118
00:07:32.270 --> 00:07:36.510
Two days in a row of Chinese food 
is too heavy, even for me.

119
00:07:36.510 --> 00:07:40.050
If it was a light Japanese meal, 
I would have been in danger.

120
00:07:40.320 --> 00:07:41.860
Right now, rather than Your Highness,

121
00:07:41.860 --> 00:07:44.850
I'm worried that the god of destruction 
may be rolling in his grave right now,

122
00:07:44.850 --> 00:07:47.480
seeing his favorite sword 
used to make fried rice.

123
00:07:48.810 --> 00:07:50.930
The heat is what makes 
or breaks fried rice!

124
00:07:50.930 --> 00:07:53.350
High temperature is what 
separates the rice granules,

125
00:07:53.350 --> 00:07:55.450
leading to perfectly delicious...

126
00:07:56.160 --> 00:07:57.270
Ah.

127
00:07:57.270 --> 00:07:58.670
The wok melted.

128
00:07:58.670 --> 00:08:01.100
Packs enough heat to melt shields!

129
00:08:03.310 --> 00:08:06.210
Why don't you ask Torture for help 
with the cooking?

130
00:08:06.210 --> 00:08:07.090
No way!

131
00:08:07.610 --> 00:08:12.180
Tor-chan's doing desk work today, 
writing up a report for her business trip.

132
00:08:12.180 --> 00:08:14.590
That's why she asked me 
to handle this torture.

133
00:08:14.860 --> 00:08:18.360
If I make her help with the torture, 
she won't finish her report...

134
00:08:18.360 --> 00:08:20.600
And she'll have to work overtime!

135
00:08:21.100 --> 00:08:23.350
We can't have that.

136
00:08:23.350 --> 00:08:27.570
That means the victor 
of today's torture is Your Highness!

137
00:08:27.570 --> 00:08:28.860
Makes sense.

138
00:08:30.910 --> 00:08:32.390
V for victory!

139
00:08:32.390 --> 00:08:34.410
Wait! Please wait, Princess!

140
00:08:34.410 --> 00:08:38.250
You're skilled enough to wield 
the legendary sacred blade Ex!

141
00:08:38.250 --> 00:08:39.530
Oh?

142
00:08:39.530 --> 00:08:43.080
You'd be able to handle this Hellblade...

143
00:08:43.080 --> 00:08:45.550
and keep the temperature 
under control, wouldn't you?!

144
00:08:47.490 --> 00:08:48.540
I'm begging you!

145
00:08:48.540 --> 00:08:51.250
Please help me make this fried rice!

146
00:08:51.250 --> 00:08:54.420
And why would we ever work with you?!

147
00:08:54.420 --> 00:08:56.070
Isn't that right, Your Highness?

148
00:08:55.450 --> 00:09:00.810
You swallowed your pride and pleaded 
with your enemy to attain your goal.

149
00:09:01.550 --> 00:09:03.200
You've got moxie!

150
00:09:03.200 --> 00:09:04.270
Your Highness?!

151
00:09:05.680 --> 00:09:07.870
Let's make that fried rice together!

152
00:09:07.870 --> 00:09:09.680
Thank you, Princess!

153
00:09:09.680 --> 00:09:11.700
She's hopeless.

154
00:09:18.680 --> 00:09:20.700
So this is Shishio's power...

155
00:09:21.440 --> 00:09:24.970
This is nothing!

156
00:09:24.970 --> 00:09:26.160
Princess...

157
00:09:26.430 --> 00:09:31.100
I am the Princess and Commander 
of the Imperial Third Legion!

158
00:09:31.100 --> 00:09:33.350
I will never bow down 
to a mere Hellblade!

159
00:09:33.860 --> 00:09:38.220
Obey me! Shishio, the Flaming Longsword!

160
00:09:45.480 --> 00:09:48.320
Yeah, that looks good in terms of heat.

161
00:09:48.320 --> 00:09:50.200
Okay, now's your chance!

162
00:09:50.200 --> 00:09:51.770
Y-Yes!

163
00:09:52.900 --> 00:09:55.410
I can smell a masterpiece cooking!

164
00:09:56.390 --> 00:09:58.190
Maintain a steady temperature!

165
00:09:58.600 --> 00:10:00.870
Speed is what makes or breaks fried rice!

166
00:10:02.200 --> 00:10:03.620
Shake that wok real good!

167
00:10:03.620 --> 00:10:04.990
Keep the rice moving!

168
00:10:04.990 --> 00:10:07.910
Finish it up by sprinkling 
in some scallions!

169
00:10:11.310 --> 00:10:12.690
All done!

170
00:10:12.690 --> 00:10:14.660
Fried rice with juicy shrimp!

171
00:10:19.470 --> 00:10:23.430
My body's craving something greasy!

172
00:10:23.430 --> 00:10:24.290
What?

173
00:10:24.290 --> 00:10:27.440
Weren't you in the mood 
for a light Japanese meal?

174
00:10:31.180 --> 00:10:33.990
Well? Did it come out good?

175
00:10:37.850 --> 00:10:38.940
I surrender!

176
00:10:38.940 --> 00:10:40.630
Yes!

177
00:10:40.630 --> 00:10:43.400
After you held your own 
against the Hellblade?!

178
00:10:44.740 --> 00:10:47.700
The princess 
confessed

179
00:10:49.630 --> 00:10:52.670
Is Gilga-chan fine on her own?

180
00:10:53.250 --> 00:10:55.210
Perhaps I should go and...

181
00:11:02.760 --> 00:11:05.430
Incoming message

182
00:11:02.760 --> 00:11:05.430
From: Gilga
 Sub: Got a secret out of her
 In the language of flowers,
 turmeric means, "The sight of
 you intoxicates me."

183
00:11:06.420 --> 00:11:09.190
It seems she succeeded 
in learning a secret.

184
00:11:09.870 --> 00:11:12.430
Good work, Gilga-chan.

185
00:11:16.940 --> 00:11:18.990
'Tis Time for "Torture,"
Princess

186
00:11:19.490 --> 00:11:21.820
Peschutz Manor

187
00:11:20.610 --> 00:11:21.830
What?!

188
00:11:22.200 --> 00:11:25.780
What did you just say, Kon-chan?

189
00:11:25.780 --> 00:11:26.630
What?

190
00:11:26.780 --> 00:11:29.040
Peschutz Manor Maid
Kon Konko

191
00:11:27.620 --> 00:11:29.040
Master said...

192
00:11:29.990 --> 00:11:32.220
It's about Vanilla-chan's tortures.

193
00:11:32.220 --> 00:11:36.800
She's been having trouble getting 
the princess to surrender as planned.

194
00:11:37.130 --> 00:11:39.480
She must be feeling dejected.

195
00:11:39.480 --> 00:11:40.760
There must be...

196
00:11:40.760 --> 00:11:44.430
a surefire torture method we 
can come up with for her.

197
00:11:44.770 --> 00:11:47.980
After hearing that, 
I simply gave you my suggestion.

198
00:11:47.980 --> 00:11:52.550
S-Still, a torture so 
terrifying and cruel...

199
00:11:52.550 --> 00:11:54.160
No...

200
00:11:54.160 --> 00:11:57.150
It's possible that I misheard you.

201
00:11:57.150 --> 00:12:01.390
Kon-chan, could you 
repeat what you just said?

202
00:12:02.040 --> 00:12:03.040
Of course.

203
00:12:03.940 --> 00:12:05.660
Jumping stairs.

204
00:12:06.110 --> 00:12:11.480
First, two people stand on the first step 
of a staircase, and proceed to jump down.

205
00:12:11.480 --> 00:12:14.310
If they succeed, then 
next is the second step.

206
00:12:14.310 --> 00:12:17.580
Then after that comes the 
third step, fourth step...

207
00:12:17.980 --> 00:12:23.390
This continues until one person is too
 scared to jump and is declared the loser.

208
00:12:23.610 --> 00:12:25.520
That's way too dangerous!

209
00:12:25.520 --> 00:12:29.520
It's what all the younger grade schoolers 
play until the teachers ban it!

210
00:12:29.520 --> 00:12:32.330
The forbidden game!

211
00:12:32.330 --> 00:12:33.690
Forbidden?

212
00:12:34.110 --> 00:12:35.990
What's wrong with that?

213
00:12:35.990 --> 00:12:37.270
Master.

214
00:12:37.270 --> 00:12:42.340
House Peschutz is said to be the most 
ruthlessly brutal clan in the Hellhorde.

215
00:12:42.340 --> 00:12:45.420
That may be true...

216
00:12:45.420 --> 00:12:49.060
But wouldn't Vanilla-chan 
be in danger as well?

217
00:12:49.350 --> 00:12:52.190
It's far from dangerous.

218
00:12:52.190 --> 00:12:55.770
Miss Vanilla is sure to 
reign victorious with this torture.

219
00:12:55.770 --> 00:12:57.300
You can't be serious!

220
00:12:57.620 --> 00:12:59.600
Have you forgotten?

221
00:12:59.600 --> 00:13:02.270
With the wings on her waist...

222
00:13:02.270 --> 00:13:04.880
Miss Vanilla can fly for 
a brief period of time!

223
00:13:04.880 --> 00:13:06.420
You're right!

224
00:13:06.800 --> 00:13:10.690
It's more like reducing her 
speed falling than flying, really.

225
00:13:10.690 --> 00:13:13.430
I see. With this...

226
00:13:14.170 --> 00:13:17.110
Vanilla-chan can be the surefire winner!

227
00:13:17.690 --> 00:13:18.920
That's right.

228
00:13:18.920 --> 00:13:21.430
There's no room for Miss Vanilla to lose!

229
00:13:21.430 --> 00:13:24.230
Unless the princess that she faces...

230
00:13:24.230 --> 00:13:27.340
has an extremely strong lower body!

231
00:13:29.280 --> 00:13:33.850
A merciless and infallible torture 
befitting the Peschutz name.

232
00:13:33.850 --> 00:13:36.070
The perfect torture!

233
00:13:36.070 --> 00:13:39.950
Unless the princess has 
an extremely strong lower body!

234
00:13:40.880 --> 00:13:44.620
I'll go suggest the idea 
to Vanilla-chan right away!

235
00:13:55.730 --> 00:13:57.030
Papa.

236
00:13:57.030 --> 00:13:58.510
Vanilla-chan.

237
00:13:59.160 --> 00:14:00.650
Are you all right?

238
00:14:00.650 --> 00:14:03.220
You looked a bit gloomy.

239
00:14:03.220 --> 00:14:04.530
Yeah.

240
00:14:04.530 --> 00:14:10.380
My tortures haven't worked out lately, 
which means I can't fail next time.

241
00:14:10.380 --> 00:14:13.370
So I was trying to come up 
with a surefire torture method.

242
00:14:13.370 --> 00:14:15.500
I-In that case...

243
00:14:17.500 --> 00:14:21.700
And just now, I had the idea 
for the best torture ever!

244
00:14:22.990 --> 00:14:24.660
Just you wait, Papa!

245
00:14:24.660 --> 00:14:27.160
I'll definitely win next time!

246
00:14:28.350 --> 00:14:29.840
This torture...

247
00:14:29.840 --> 00:14:33.060
I hope the princess likes it.

248
00:14:34.680 --> 00:14:35.970
Oh yeah, Papa.

249
00:14:35.970 --> 00:14:37.260
What did you want?

250
00:14:38.530 --> 00:14:39.460
No...

251
00:14:40.850 --> 00:14:42.480
It's nothing.

252
00:14:42.770 --> 00:14:45.610
I'm sure the princess will love it.

253
00:14:45.610 --> 00:14:46.690
Yeah!

254
00:14:46.690 --> 00:14:52.690
Since I, the daughter of the noble House
of Peschutz, came up with this torture!

255
00:14:57.260 --> 00:15:00.290
Time for your torture, Princess!

256
00:15:00.290 --> 00:15:07.250
I, the daughter of the House of Peschutz, 
have devised the perfect torture for you!

257
00:15:07.250 --> 00:15:10.350
Vanilla-chan, you seem different today.

258
00:15:10.350 --> 00:15:13.070
We'll need to brace ourselves.

259
00:15:14.810 --> 00:15:17.020
Nothing will have you ready for this one.

260
00:15:17.020 --> 00:15:19.270
Today's torture is utterly flawless!

261
00:15:19.990 --> 00:15:22.140
<i>Mama and Papa said it was great!</i>

262
00:15:22.530 --> 00:15:25.650
<i>And I picked a really 
cute gift bag for it.</i>

263
00:15:26.110 --> 00:15:29.150
You're sure to surrender
 completely, Princess!

264
00:15:29.660 --> 00:15:35.780
Even I had to admire its sheer perfection 
next to my pillow just before I slept!

265
00:15:35.780 --> 00:15:37.170
Sheer perfection?

266
00:15:37.550 --> 00:15:39.620
Just what does this torture entail?!

267
00:15:40.580 --> 00:15:42.210
Wouldn't you like to know?

268
00:15:42.650 --> 00:15:45.370
Why don't I show you right now?

269
00:15:45.630 --> 00:15:46.930
Take this!

270
00:15:46.930 --> 00:15:50.920
Here's your torture for today!

271
00:16:01.290 --> 00:16:05.580
I left the torture next to my pillow...

272
00:16:05.580 --> 00:16:06.390
What?

273
00:16:08.020 --> 00:16:09.750
W-Wait, Princess!

274
00:16:09.750 --> 00:16:11.450
I'll go grab it right now!

275
00:16:11.450 --> 00:16:12.870
Vanilla-chan!

276
00:16:24.290 --> 00:16:27.090
<i>It was the perfect torture, too...</i>

277
00:16:32.810 --> 00:16:36.680
<i>I worked so hard late into the night...</i>

278
00:16:49.110 --> 00:16:51.030
<i>Now that's what I call merciless!</i>

279
00:16:51.030 --> 00:16:54.340
<i>What a wonderful torture 
that lives up to the Peschutz name!</i>

280
00:16:54.340 --> 00:16:56.760
<i>That's my Vanilla-chan!</i>

281
00:16:59.340 --> 00:17:02.970
<i>After all the praise I got 
from Mama and Papa...</i>

282
00:17:05.530 --> 00:17:07.390
Sorry to make you carry me like this.

283
00:17:07.390 --> 00:17:09.870
You need a chaperone in order 
to leave the castle.

284
00:17:09.870 --> 00:17:11.350
Don't sweat it.

285
00:17:11.350 --> 00:17:12.920
Thanks for coming along.

286
00:17:13.790 --> 00:17:15.920
Found her! Vanilla-chan!

287
00:17:17.510 --> 00:17:19.870
I knew it! Vanilla-chan's crying!

288
00:17:32.700 --> 00:17:34.190
<i>It's okay!</i>

289
00:17:34.190 --> 00:17:36.850
<i>The torture hasn't failed yet!</i>

290
00:17:36.850 --> 00:17:39.530
<i>If I run to grab it 
and head back, I can make it!</i>

291
00:17:40.260 --> 00:17:42.590
<i>You can do it, Vanilla!</i>

292
00:17:45.750 --> 00:17:48.320
Is Vanilla-chan's house far from here?

293
00:17:48.320 --> 00:17:51.550
'Tis about a ten-minute 
walk from Hellholm.

294
00:17:51.550 --> 00:17:53.210
I wouldn't call it far.

295
00:17:53.610 --> 00:17:54.670
I see.

296
00:17:55.580 --> 00:17:58.150
Should we head back and wait, then?

297
00:17:58.150 --> 00:17:59.710
Yes, let's do that.

298
00:18:02.660 --> 00:18:04.140
Princess!

299
00:18:04.140 --> 00:18:06.640
Once again, it's time for your torture!

300
00:18:06.940 --> 00:18:09.790
Let's see it, then.

301
00:18:09.790 --> 00:18:12.240
Let's test this perfect torture of yours!

302
00:18:12.510 --> 00:18:16.900
Here's your torture for today!

303
00:18:18.930 --> 00:18:20.850
Whoa, what's this?

304
00:18:20.850 --> 00:18:22.280
This gift bag's so cute!

305
00:18:23.620 --> 00:18:24.950
Open it up.

306
00:18:24.950 --> 00:18:26.690
What could it be?

307
00:18:29.660 --> 00:18:31.510
A teddy bear!

308
00:18:31.510 --> 00:18:34.410
Wait, don't tell me that it's...

309
00:18:38.740 --> 00:18:40.170
Sewn by hand.

310
00:18:40.170 --> 00:18:41.070
What?!

311
00:18:41.070 --> 00:18:44.290
Surrendering's not enough for this!

312
00:18:44.590 --> 00:18:46.560
Thanks, Vanilla-chan!

313
00:18:47.350 --> 00:18:48.230
Yeah.

314
00:18:53.190 --> 00:18:59.410
Today's inquisitor, Vanilla Peschutz, 
successfully made the princess yield.

315
00:19:01.200 --> 00:19:04.290
I'd expect no less from Aliotto's girl.

316
00:19:04.290 --> 00:19:08.780
She can't resist her 
diabolical Peschutz blood.

317
00:19:08.780 --> 00:19:09.840
Well said!

318
00:19:09.840 --> 00:19:12.100
As for the information she obtained...

319
00:19:13.760 --> 00:19:18.540
It seems the princess's little sister 
sleeps with a stuffed animal every night.

320
00:19:23.620 --> 00:19:25.460
I approve!

321
00:21:01.560 --> 00:21:04.700
<i>Wow, I really like how this looks.</i>

322
00:21:04.700 --> 00:21:06.820
<i>And it feels great to the touch.</i>

323
00:21:06.820 --> 00:21:09.940
<i>The price... seems reasonable!</i>

324
00:21:10.560 --> 00:21:13.090
I'll go grab you a new one.

325
00:21:13.090 --> 00:21:17.530
<i>It's my first time in here, 
but it turned out to be a great shop.</i>

326
00:21:17.530 --> 00:21:21.040
That comes out to 34,200 yen.

327
00:21:22.810 --> 00:21:23.640
Eh?

328
00:21:32.000 --> 00:21:36.730
<i>My purchase yesterday turned out 
to cost more than I thought.</i>

329
00:21:37.390 --> 00:21:39.710
<i>I mean, I like the color...</i>

330
00:21:39.710 --> 00:21:41.530
<i>And the material is nice...</i>

331
00:21:42.300 --> 00:21:46.200
<i>But 30,000 yen for a completely 
normal-looking sweatshirt...</i>

332
00:21:46.920 --> 00:21:52.030
<i>I was too embarrassed to say, 
"Actually, never mind" at the register...</i>

333
00:21:52.270 --> 00:21:55.400
No, there's no point in moping like this!

334
00:21:55.400 --> 00:21:58.360
This doesn't change the fact 
that it's a nice piece of clothing!

335
00:21:58.360 --> 00:22:00.550
I'll go out today wearing this!

336
00:22:08.290 --> 00:22:12.980
<i>The material is thin and light, 
yet I'm so warm with this one layer alone!</i>

337
00:22:14.530 --> 00:22:16.750
<i>And it feels so nice on my body.</i>

338
00:22:17.260 --> 00:22:18.880
<i>I never knew...</i>

339
00:22:19.430 --> 00:22:23.010
<i>Good quality fabric... really </i>is<i> good!</i>

340
00:22:27.670 --> 00:22:30.400
<i>I feel like there's more 
bounce in my step today.</i>

341
00:22:30.910 --> 00:22:36.620
<i>Fashion's about more than just the price, 
but I still feel a sense of exhilaration.</i>

342
00:22:37.340 --> 00:22:38.900
<i>At this very moment...</i>

343
00:22:39.250 --> 00:22:41.560
<i>I'm wearing some nice clothes!</i>

344
00:22:47.360 --> 00:22:49.590
<i>Oh yes, this hotel...</i>

345
00:22:49.590 --> 00:22:51.700
<i>I believe they have a café.</i>

346
00:22:52.880 --> 00:22:56.350
<i>It always seemed too upscale 
for me to go inside,</i>

347
00:22:57.000 --> 00:22:59.840
<i>but I feel like I can work up 
the courage now!</i>

348
00:23:00.530 --> 00:23:03.290
<i>Seeing as how I'm wearing nice clothes!</i>

349
00:23:07.420 --> 00:23:09.180
This is great!

350
00:23:13.220 --> 00:23:17.030
<i>Today was a fun day 
full of new experiences.</i>

351
00:23:17.590 --> 00:23:21.510
<i>I never saw the point in buying 
expensive casual clothes before...</i>

352
00:23:22.710 --> 00:23:25.010
<i>But it turned out to have its merits.</i>

353
00:23:25.010 --> 00:23:27.300
<i>I learned something new today.</i>

354
00:23:27.300 --> 00:23:30.050
<i>It's always good to approach things 
with an open mind.</i>

355
00:23:30.870 --> 00:23:35.710
<i>I'll buy the clothes I like best 
going forward, regardless of the price...</i>

356
00:23:38.420 --> 00:23:43.420
Created by ©Yozuki  |  #VisitUs  t.me/Yozukilk

357
00:23:40.910 --> 00:23:43.420
Let's take good care of this sweatshirt.

